{"tid":2451532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【拜習會面】北京計劃於四月與拜登會面","createTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:29.000Z","uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d17a1c367ca117c93b1e779e7a55cdd546001d5","tid":2451532,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"根據線人提供，若禮拜四嘅阿拉斯加州中美會談舉行順利，北京將於四月與拜登會面。<br />\n<br />\n線人指，中國官員預定於地球日（四月廿二號）舉行拜習會面，以表雙方領袖都重視氣候變化問題。拜登已準備於當日聚集各國領袖，以推進全球遏制溫室氣體排放問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-18/china-seeks-biden-xi-meeting-next-month-if-alaska-talks-go-well\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-03-18%2Fchina-seeks-biden-xi-meeting-next-month-if-alaska-talks-go-well&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2dg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=76d6bda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-18/china-seeks-biden-xi-meeting-next-month-if-alaska-talks-go-well</a>"}]}